  "general_provisions": "This bill amends the class size reduction appropriation.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>renames the appropriation;<hr><ltbullet>modifies provisions regarding the use of class size reduction funding;<hr><ltbullet>modifies which grade levels the program applies to;<hr><ltbullet>requires a local education agency to establish and maintain certain policies regarding teacher to student ratios;<hr><ltbullet>expands permitted uses of the allocation to include certain staff supports;<hr><ltbullet>establishes reporting requirements;<hr><ltbullet>requires certain information to be publicly available; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical changes.",
